{"tid":1822352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係時候重溫梁天琦封信","createTime":"2020-01-13T02:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T14:32:02.000Z","uid":48064,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d3584db0ab18a2038d47230c916cd1860d740c","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"但願我這封信不會來得太遲。<br />\n<br />\n這個夏天炎熱而漫長。每逢周末晚上，我都總會戴上耳機，收聽電台的新聞簡報，憂心香港局勢發展。隔天早上，我就會看到電視的早晨新聞，臨近中午就會讀到報章報道。一次又一次，我看著這些血迹斑斑的畫面，內心滿是悲哀和苦痛。<br />\n<br />\n我知道，我怎樣努力都無法想像你們正在經歷的苦難和身心承受的傷痛。在槍林彈雨中，親眼目睹鮮血灑在街頭，聽見四周的哀嚎吶喊，定必使你們悲憤不已。<br />\n<br />\n隨著被捕和送院的數字不斷遞增，我想到你們要面對的將來，和那些難以癒合的傷口，我很想知道，究竟有誰能夠撫平這個社會的創傷。<br />\n<br />\n我與社會隔絕了已經一年半有多，接收的資訊極其有限，我在這個位置寫這封信，妄加評論，未免過於廉價。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，我仍希望你們能夠明白：本著對香港的熱愛，你們已展現了無比的勇氣，改寫了香港的歷史。當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。<br />\n<br />\n我衷心祈求每個香港人都能夠平安渡過這個歷史關口。<br />\n<br />\n2019 年 7 月 28 日<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n係高登年代開始做左十年cdrom 都忍唔住<br />\n<br />\n成班係出面話影人大頭係做乜鳩？<br />\n係到人民鬥人民<br />\n之後就用輸民意黎包裝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前點解比人屌話輸民意先<br />\n係因為打人入鏡畫面唔好睇<br />\n但係個班係打手足斬到手足流曬血無人執法先做<br />\n<br />\n一係就係奶共<span style=\"color: red;\">企業</span>先裝修<br />\n<br />\n而家你同我因為佢食元氣就影大頭？再用輸民意做藉口？你覺得影人就可以影到佢地覺醒一齊對抗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">訓撚醒未呀屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"2524160c2fb8bd171c2232e93e7cc0809a223dde","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0725fc13425c2b5f209132f5e6bc2264883c3be1","tid":1822352,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:16:34.000Z","msg":"cc台軍師：樓主咁耐以嚟得一個po，肯定係五毛嚟，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caa03b276b95c9a47fc2a8e121a74848f48c56c","tid":1822352,"uid":55669,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e62297f47348dd4f575c0e0df0c82d14390f18","tid":1822352,"uid":55669,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e2a3ed37e8f89c7a6d2effbc74bde1c5690b92","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0725fc13425c2b5f209132f5e6bc2264883c3be1","tid":1822352,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:16:34.000Z","msg":"cc台軍師：樓主咁耐以嚟得一個po，肯定係五毛嚟，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"屌我都覺會比人當五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係覺得大家已經唔記得一路以黎我地點行到今日<br />\n所以先開po <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d4af64d849d70b583e8f1db62a73448922935f","tid":1822352,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"天琦個刑期上訴幾時有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52e5eddbe3eec9598dc81fdf52b27c4b66f995","tid":1822352,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"5毛 拉"},{"pid":"55fb58f7bb9f10cd98cac064e24c7c2138946f26","tid":1822352,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。"},{"pid":"0c698634164ae1914a27e49d7c039fe53219a62d","tid":1822352,"uid":219256,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635eb32cae041f1566a661016e5c14645d59a184","tid":1822352,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5341678c9abe251ce8398277a1dc51cdf7f94c17","tid":1822352,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"出面世界大戰，天琦的話好重要"},{"pid":"ea697905733f8ea9e54f3550d05d2e66fbd03e14","tid":1822352,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"cc台班言論糾察隊咪最鍾意四處得罪人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d637c1ed41c56aa45617bcfa296ddd7f1b3743f0","tid":1822352,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"從溫佢上次個speech"},{"pid":"05a04daab867c80dc575ef6b66d2caadd9459705","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"849ab8a4820e205b7c2c74e6c27d2f5f4fcdf0c1","tid":1822352,"uid":147880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1ceb330a3bb9d68d746302711f83d88485ccf0b","tid":1822352,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea697905733f8ea9e54f3550d05d2e66fbd03e14","tid":1822352,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"cc台班言論糾察隊咪最鍾意四處得罪人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"左膠：令支持自己嘅人離開自己，換取其他唔支持自己嘅人支持自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd6a46f1e97839b55a0879ac18c4ffcb3aea4ee","tid":1822352,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f8c1e960c1057f35830b892418dfb974e220701","tid":1822352,"uid":258820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都推"},{"pid":"42fa8feaea59b1f7d11e90e6f6f718a0199016dd","tid":1822352,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8272ceea73b5cd19f10bd02158cf3cc4220e06f0","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efffef78842112fee3c54abd29530e2b39cce025","tid":1822352,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0ba8a45903a59ae4619934934c27817dbeb8776","tid":1822352,"uid":306621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:37:41.000Z","msg":"未進化左膠<br />\n不如等香港變成新疆先抗爭啦<br />\n<br />\n幫襯藍店同比錢對家打鳩我地有咩分別"},{"pid":"3abe930343763429e0a0128c710232a4d8cfb19c","tid":1822352,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"個個人做到嘅程度唔同<br />\n好似我罷到鐵罷到藍店罷唔到八達通<br />\n咁人地係想食藍店都無計 可能人地另一方面有付出<br />\n然後你就屌柒佢影佢相割佢蓆<br />\n我地要做既唔係樹立更多敵人<br />\n各有各做呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁有心不如痴多兩張文宣"},{"pid":"8c8b10273fcd0be7631886a146fef20287d30a6c","tid":1822352,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"以cctai標準梁天琦一定又係左膠五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}